data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select "OrderPayment".*, "Order".*, "Unit".*, "Client".* from ((("dbo"."OrderPayment" "OrderPayment" FULL join "dbo"."Order" "Order" on ("Order"."OrderId" = "OrderPayment"."OrderId")) FULL join "dbo"."Unit" "Unit" on ("Unit"."UnitId" = "Order"."UnitId")) FULL join "dbo"."Client" "Client" on ("Client"."ClientId" = "Order"."ClientId"))WHERE "OrderPayment"."IsEnabled" = '1' AND "OrderPayment"."IsDeleted" = '0'
